{"tid":2507450,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓價指數】3月租金指數報174.8點 終止3個月跌勢","createTime":"2021-04-28T04:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T04:40:22.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4352243ccbf6fbfa685f17c0bc9617a1212cb3e7","tid":2507450,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"【樓價指數】3月租金指數報174.8點 終止3個月跌勢<br />\n11:12 2021/04/28<br />\n<br />\n&quot;差餉物業估價署最新數據顯示，樓價指數按月升0.8%，另一方面，租金指數同錄升幅，今年3月份租金指數報174.8點，較2月的173.7點，輕微升約0.6%，終止連續3個月跌勢......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2943381/%E3%80%90%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E3%80%913%E6%9C%88%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E5%A0%B1174.8%E9%BB%9E%20%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A23%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E8%B7%8C%E5%8B%A2?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2943381%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2595%25B8%25E3%2580%25913%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25A0%25B1174.8%25E9%25BB%259E%2520%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25AD%25A23%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%258B%25A2%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0vQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=783aa336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2943381/%E3%80%90%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E3%80%913%E6%9C%88%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E5%A0%B1174.8%E9%BB%9E%20%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A23%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E8%B7%8C%E5%8B%A2?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">對投資客係好消息，對租客係壞消息</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8a05c7a63980339a12eb610cf3865014588d3d07","tid":2507450,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"上月簽租約集D肥肥la"},{"pid":"ff781f922e74e1d0142a665709166bfa546fa04a","tid":2507450,"uid":362300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"韓林兒不開的post"},{"pid":"099ddf4a740ad6d27b8b47db14050594a6ec46ad","tid":2507450,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff781f922e74e1d0142a665709166bfa546fa04a","tid":2507450,"uid":362300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"韓林兒不開的post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"等打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb538547208f388d4bcc8697213ef8f127e913a","tid":2507450,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"差估署：3月私宅租金指數按年跌近3.8%<br />\n<br />\n差餉物業估價署公布的最新數據顯示，今年3月私人住宅租金指數按月回升0.63%至174.8，結束3個月跌勢；較去年同期仍低3.79%。<br />\n<br />\n該月私人住宅售價指數報388.3點，按月升約0.8%，已連升3個月，為2019年7月後的20個月新高。<br />\n<br />\n至於今年首季售價指數則上升約2.2%，而去年首季同類指數仍下跌約0.2%，反映今年樓價走勢明顯改善。而今年1至3月份租金指數則仍挫約1%，去年同期該指數跌幅達約4.2%。<br />\n<br />\n當月兩類面積單位樓價均報升，當中實用面積約1,075方呎以上大型住宅單位走勢較好，上月指數報326.2點，較2月份上升約0.9%，首季則漲約2.5%。實用面積約1,075方呎及以下中小型單位售價指數報390.8點，按月上升約0.8%，今年首季累升約2.2%。"}]}